                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar__logout-box">
            <form action="/auth/logout" method="POST">
                <label for="logout">
                    <i class='bx bx-log-out sidebar__logout-icon'></i>
                </label>
                <button type="submit" style="visibility:hidden" id="logout" name="logout">
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main__big-container">
        <div class="main__container">
            <div class="main__box">
                <h1 class="main__title">Componente HEADER</h1>
                <p class="main__description">üõ†Ô∏è Edita aqu√≠ todo lo relacionado con el header de tu sitio:</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="main__container">
            <div class="main__box">
